ğŸ—£ï¸ RoboSpeaker 1.1 â€“ Text to Speech using Python

RoboSpeaker is a simple Text-to-Speech (TTS) program built using Python and Windows PowerShell.
It converts user-entered text into speech using the System.Speech API.

ğŸš€ Features

Converts text input into spoken voice

Continuous input using a loop

Exit command with farewell message

Uses built-in Windows speech engine

Lightweight & beginner-friendly

ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used

Python 3

Windows PowerShell

System.Speech.Synthesis (Windows API)

âš ï¸ Works on Windows only

