ğŸ“œ How It Works

User enters text in the terminal

Python sends the text to PowerShell

PowerShell uses System.Speech.Synthesis

Computer speaks the entered text

Typing exit stops the program

â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Project
1ï¸âƒ£ Ensure Python is Installed

